{"tid":1862418,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"英皇集團捐千萬元物資及捐款 支持湖北及香港緊急防疫工作","createTime":"2020-02-04T15:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T05:01:27.000Z","uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fd132d9b9981196822139a5580a756b6bbf3764d","tid":1862418,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"英皇集團捐千萬元物資及捐款 支持湖北及香港緊急防疫工作<br />\n齊心抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n面對新型肺炎疫情持續蔓延，英皇集團連日與湖北省慈善總會及無國界社工緊密溝通協調，宣佈通過英皇慈善基金向湖北省慈善總會及無國界社工，捐贈合共人民幣1000萬元的醫療防護物資及捐款，以支持湖北省及香港的緊急防疫工作，其中包括過百部無創呼吸機用於支持對症治療，以輔助重病患者增加有效的通氣量、改善換氣；另採購過萬套醫療防護裝備，為湖北省醫療單位、堅守崗位的一線支持人員及重病患者提供支持和幫助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/01/200130_CR_%E8%8B%B1%E7%9A%872.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F01%2F200130_CR_%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%259A%25872.jpg&h=f5f3f328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英皇集團的孤老善養服務一直與無國界社工合作，在湖北省多個城市進行外展服務。<br />\n<br />\n物資經已搜購並將於下星期抵達湖北省，並報送至湖北省新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控指揮部，再分配給湖北省內9個市縣十多家嚴重缺乏醫療設備的醫院。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/01/200130_CR_%E8%8B%B1%E7%9A%87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F01%2F200130_CR_%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%259A%2587.jpg&h=13e29741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無創呼吸機及防護裝備，陸續送到湖北省醫院。<br />\n<br />\n部分捐款將分別捐贈至湖北省慈善總會及香港無國界社工，前者通過其省級統籌管理能力，有效地統一調配各類資源，用於多層面的抗疫行動；無國界社工則透過與香港社區合作，為社區獨居老人及基層家庭分派緊急防疫物資，進行社區防疫教育。"},{"pid":"ff8f870410636c6acd57a569ad87c327ee3aa084","tid":1862418,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"代表支那高官多謝楊老闆"},{"pid":"2e08df04a8688342b3c2e98301c72eed27004887","tid":1862418,"uid":160847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff8f870410636c6acd57a569ad87c327ee3aa084","tid":1862418,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"代表支那高官多謝楊老闆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:25:55.000Z","msg":"正，每個又分到幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafd8782788405ca1bf992de83cc09147a927787","tid":1862418,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:30:51.000Z","msg":"買命錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01adca92db513272316aa3e814f58510d2b1191","tid":1862418,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:01:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當年</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaUgNwQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaUgNwQ.png&h=6d2974dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加入英蝗後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SAwBsuQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSAwBsuQ.png&h=f36299a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">曾樂彤經理人：黃絲廢青 不喜歡就不要看</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtjNMPn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtjNMPn.png&h=5bcc4ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NB2C82J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNB2C82J.png&h=0bd6199f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}